venture television series Diriliş: Ertuğrul from 2014 to 2018. As of now, the actress is playing the main lead in the Turkish crime drama series Ramo.\r\n\r\nEsra Bilgic Age:\r\nThe Turkish actress was born on October 14, 1992, in Ankara, Turkey. She will be turning 28 this year, for now, the actress is still 27. At such a young age, Esra has conquered the entertainment industry worldwide. She is known for her beautiful and expressive eyes as well as for her natural beauty. Bilgic is a nature lover and in her leisure time, she loves to spend time at beaches.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nEsra Bilgic Nationality, Height & Weight:\r\nThe beautiful actress was born in Turkey’s most beautiful city Ankara, which makes her hold Turkish nationality. According to details, Esra is 5 feet and 10 inches tall. Just like her powerful personality, the actress weighs 68 kgs and wears a size 4 (US) dress. The actress has maintained her health by working out and eating healthy. The Ankara native has beautiful dark brown eyes that shine brighter than a diamond. especially in the sunlight.', 'esra-bilgic-untold-facts-about-the-turkish-actress', 12, 1, 'post_main49.jpg', 'post_thumb49.jpg', 'post_list49.jpg', 0, 0, 1, 0, '2020-07-11 05:41:22', '2020-07-11 05:41:22'),
(50, 'TikTok Star Jannat Mirza’s Song Will Release This Friday', 'Many people have gained popularity through an entertainment App “TikTok”. Some of the TikTokers drew the attention of the media industry’s giants and bagged a part in different projects.\r\n\r\nRecently TikTok star Areeka Haq appeared in Asim Azhar’s new song video “Tum Tum” and Zulqarnain Sikander got a chance to act in Aqeel Tashi’s movie “Master and Company”.', 'Many people have gained popularity through an entertainment App “TikTok”. Some of the TikTokers drew the attention of the media industry’s giants and bagged a part in different projects.\r\n\r\nRecently TikTok star Areeka Haq appeared in Asim Azhar’s new song video “Tum Tum” and Zulqarnain Sikander got a chance to act in Aqeel Tashi’s movie “Master and Company”.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAnother TikTok celebrity Jannat Mirza, the most follower TikToker in Pakistan, has got an opportunity to appear in a song video “Shayar”.\r\n\r\nThe song is sung by renowned Pakistani singer Bilal Saeed and it depicts a poet’s journey being torn between reality and dreams.\r\n\r\nJannat took to her Instagram account and revealed the song will be released on Friday. She wrote,\r\n\r\n“ONE DAY TO GO. SHAYAR. 10-07-20”', 'tiktok-star-jannat-mirzas-song-will-release-this-friday', 12, 1, 'post_main50.jpg', 'post_thumb50.jpg', 'post_list50.jpg', 0, 0, 1, 0, '2020-07-11 05:44:06', '2020-07-11 05:44:53'),
(51, 'Britney Spears Appears In Instagram’s Q&A Session, Reveals Her Three Wishes', 'America’s singing sensation Britney Spears has appeared in quick Q&A session with her fans, revealing that her three desires would be love, happiness and a world supply of designer clothes.\r\n\r\nThe singer has recently sparked concern among her admirers, as #FreeBritney begins to trend again.\r\n\r\nSpears rocked a cropped floral white blouse in the video, saying: “So, a lot of my fans have been asking me a lot of questions during my comments. I listened, and so now, I’m going to answer all of your questions.”', 'America’s singing sensation Britney Spears has appeared in quick Q&A session with her fans, revealing that her three desires would be love, happiness and a world supply of designer clothes.\r\n\r\nThe singer has recently sparked concern among her admirers, as #FreeBritney begins to trend again.\r\n\r\nSpears rocked a cropped floral white blouse in the video, saying: “So, a lot of my fans have been asking me a lot of questions during my comments. I listened, and so now, I’m going to answer all of your questions.”\r\n\r\n\r\nShe first answered about her favorite song: ‘My favorite song is Toxic, that I’ve done. And I have no idea what my favorite song in the whole world is.’\r\n\r\nShe then revealed her favorite vacation spot: ‘My favorite place to visit is Hawaii and Turks and Caicos. Turks and Caicos is a little bit more jungley and more tropical.’\r\n\r\nBritney Spears spent holidays in Hawaii back in February with boyfriend Sam Asghari and she enjoyed a getaway last June to Turks and Caicos with her mom Lynne.\r\n\r\nBritney with a smile like a big foodie, stated: ‘What’s my favorite food? It’s a chili hot dog.’\r\n\r\nALSO READ\r\n\r\n\r\nEarlier, Britney Spears had spent some quality time with her beau Sam Asghari at the beach, following safety precautions due to Coronavirus.\r\n\r\nSpears and Sam paired their swimsuits with masks for the outing to make sure they were safe during a trip to the beach.\r\n\r\nThe singer, shared several pictures from their beach day on Instagram. She captioned the post, “All you need is love and the beach.”', 'britney-spears-appears-in-instagrams-qa-session-reveals-her-three-wishes', 12, 11, 'post_main51.jpg', 'post_thumb51.jpg', 'post_list51.jpg', 0, 0, 1, 0, '2020-07-11 05:46:23', '2020-07-11 05:46:23'),
(52, 'Ali Zafar Details Comments About PSL Anthem Controversy', 'A name that needs to introduction, Ali Zafar has multitudes of talents through which he can easily impress his audience and fans.\r\n\r\nSpeaking about the voice magic of Ali Zafar, we all know that Pakistan Super League songs, Dil Se Jaan Laga De, Ab Khel Kay Dikha and Seeti Bajay Gi happen to be three iconic PSL anthems, all sung by the singer during the first three years of the league.\r\n\r\nIn PSL’s 4th season, the singer was replaced by Fawad Khan and the fifth season saw Asim Azhar, Arif Lohar and Ali Azmat made a joint effort with for the anthem.', 'A name that needs to introduction, Ali Zafar has multitudes of talents through which he can easily impress his audience and fans.\r\n\r\nSpeaking about the voice magic of Ali Zafar, we all know that Pakistan Super League songs, Dil Se Jaan Laga De, Ab Khel Kay Dikha and Seeti Bajay Gi happen to be three iconic PSL anthems, all sung by the singer during the first three years of the league.\r\n\r\nIn PSL’s 4th season, the singer was replaced by Fawad Khan and the fifth season saw Asim Azhar, Arif Lohar and Ali Azmat made a joint effort with for the anthem.\r\n\r\n‘Tayyar Hain’ – PSL 5 Anthem:\r\n\r\n\r\nHowever, as per the opinions by fans and viewers, none of the songs became as popular as Ali Zafar’s tracks.\r\n\r\nMoreover, addressing why he didn’t sing the anthems for PSL season 4 and 5, Ali Zafar in a live chat stated: “I hadn’t wanted to do the 2nd and 3rd PSL anthem but I did and they became huge hits after the first one. However, for the 4th and 5th season, the PCB seem to have their own reasons and preferences for the singer and I totally respect that.” Zafar further added on to state how he couldn’t force the board for anything.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nMoreover, netizens, after the flop PSL 5 anthem, requested Ali Zafar to release his own track. The request came forward as ‘Mela Loot Liya‘ which now has crossed 8 million plus views on YouTube.\r\n\r\n‘Mela Loot Liya’ By Ali Zafar', 'ali-zafar-details-comments-about-psl-anthem-controversy', 12, 11, 'post_main52.jpeg', 'post_thumb52.jpeg', 'post_list52.jpeg', 0, 0, 1, 1, '2020-07-11 05:47:29', '2020-07-22 13:27:58'),
(53, 'How Pakistani Celebrity Couples Are Spending Self Quarantine Time?', 'Many countries around the world are observing complete lockdowns due to the novel coronavirus. People have self quarantined themselves for not getting in contact with the deadly virus.\r\n\r\nHowever, in Pakistan where people can not survive without stepping out on the streets, many find such a time at home quite hard. Yet many Pakistani celebrity couples have found ways to spend their time at home.\r\n\r\nHere is how Pakistani celebrity couples are spending their time during the ongoing pandemic.', 'Many countries around the world are observing complete lockdowns due to the novel coronavirus. People have self quarantined themselves for not getting in contact with the deadly virus.\r\n\r\nHowever, in Pakistan where people can not survive without stepping out on the streets, many find such a time at home quite hard. Yet many Pakistani celebrity couples have found ways to spend their time at home.\r\n\r\nHere is how Pakistani celebrity couples are spending their time during the ongoing pandemic.', 'how-pakistani-celebrity-couples-are-spending-self-quarantine-time', 12, 11, 'post_main53.jpg', 'post_thumb53.jpg', 'post_list53.jpg', 0, 0, 1, 1, '2020-07-11 05:48:27', '2020-07-22 13:19:55'),
(55, 'Factors That Cause Premature Ageing', 'Do you look older than your age? If so, regardless of genetic complications, there are many elements of daily life that cause premature ageing.\r\n\r\nIf you do not want to see such a scene in the mirror, then changing your daily habits will be the best way.\r\n\r\nHere we introduce the methods and habits that lead to ageing. These habits are as follows.', 'Do you look older than your age? If so, regardless of genetic complications, there are many elements of daily life that cause premature ageing.\r\n\r\nIf you do not want to see such a scene in the mirror, then changing your daily habits will be the best way.\r\n\r\nHere we introduce the methods and habits that lead to ageing. These habits are as follows.\r\n\r\nLack of Omega-3 fatty acids in Diet\r\n\r\nTo avoid wrinkles in the third or fourth decade of life, it is important to include omega-3 fatty acids in your diet to keep the skin smooth and healthy. If the diet is low fat then we will be deprived of omega 3 fatty acids which will result in premature ageing.\r\n\r\nLack of Omega-3 fatty acids in Diet\r\n\r\nSleeping sideways\r\n\r\nSleeping sideways When your face is tucked into a pillow on one side which increases the risk of wrinkles on the cheeks and chin, medical experts say that lying down is the best way to sleep. Keeps the body young, fresh and calm.\r\n\r\nSleeping sideways\r\n\r\nSitting for long periods\r\nSitting too much throughout the day makes you age prematurely. It has already been proven that sitting for too long can lead to many diseases such as obesity, heart disease, diabetes, cancer and even premature death. But recent research has shown that sitting for long periods of time has a negative effect on the human body.\r\nSitting for long periods\r\nExcessive sugar consumption\r\nExcessive sugar consumption increases your body weight as well as causes premature ageing. Sugar attaches to our cells and as a result, the redness disappears from the face and dark circles appear under the eyes. Similarly, wrinkles and light lines make the face look old. It’s not like you can completely eliminate sugar from your life, but avoiding sweets can help keep your face glowing.\r\n  Excessive sugar consumption\r\nLack of sleep\r\nLess sleep not only causes dark circles around the eyes but also shortens the life span. The habit of getting less than seven hours of sleep a night can lead to low energy, lethargy, difficulty concentrating or obesity throughout the day.\r\nLack of sleep\r\nMental stress\r\nNumerous research reports have shown that excessive stress can cause serious damage to body cells and accelerate the ageing process. Severe stress on a long-term basis makes you look old at a young age.\r\n  Mental stress', 'factors-that-cause-premature-ageing', 13, 9, 'post_main55.jpg', 'post_thumb55.jpg', 'post_list55.jpg', 38, 0, 1, 0, '2020-07-11 05:58:59', '2021-07-28 02:54:20'),
(56, 'Twitter Will Introduce Its Edit Button When Everyone Wears A Mask', 'The social media website Twitter has put in a condition before adding the much-awaited “edit” button.\r\n\r\nThe tweet from the company’s official account prompted a torrent of responses and in less than 24 hours it received about two million likes.\r\n\r\nTwitter’s official handle on Thursday night wrote in a tweet,\r\n\r\n“You can have an edit button when everyone wears a mask.”\r\n\r\nYou can have an edit button when everyone wears a mask\r\n\r\n— Twitter (@Twitter) July 2, 2020', 'The social media website Twitter has put in a condition before adding the much-awaited “edit” button.\r\n\r\nThe tweet from the company’s official account prompted a torrent of responses and in less than 24 hours it received about two million likes.\r\n\r\nTwitter’s official handle on Thursday night wrote in a tweet,\r\n\r\n“You can have an edit button when everyone wears a mask.”\r\n\r\nYou can have an edit button when everyone wears a mask\r\n\r\n— Twitter (@Twitter) July 2, 2020\r\n\r\nIn less than 24 hours, the tweet received nearly 2 million likes and sparked all sorts of reactions. Some people said Twitter is fine without it, although others were disappointed.\r\n\r\nIt is pertinent to mention here that earlier this year, Twitter co-founder Jack Dorsey had said that the company would “probably never” introduce the feature because it may unintentionally cause misinformation to spread to users.', 'twitter-will-introduce-its-edit-button-when-everyone-wears-a-mask', 14, 9, 'post_main56.jpg', 'post_thumb56.jpg', 'post_list56.jpg', 0, 1, 1, 0, '2020-07-11 06:01:07', '2020-07-22 12:35:41'),
(57, '5 Tips To Work Effectively From Home', '<p>Due to the spread of novel coronavirus, people are forced to stay at home for their own and others&rsquo; safety. Due to the lockdown in different parts of the world, many people are encouraged to even do their office work from home. Many people find it difficult to concentrate on work while being at home as the work environment and home environment are totally different. Here are some tips that will help you work effectively from home if you are still not comfortable with this new routine.</p>', '<p>Due to the spread of novel coronavirus, people are forced to stay at home for their own and others&rsquo; safety. Due to the lockdown in different parts of the world, many people are encouraged to even do their office work from home. Many people find it difficult to concentrate on work while being at home as the work environment and home environment are totally different. Here are some tips that will help you work effectively from home if you are still not comfortable with this new routine. Continue Your Daily Routine: Just because you&rsquo;re not traveling and going to an office doesn&rsquo;t mean you&rsquo;re expected to miss your regular weekday preparations. Wake up, shower, and get dressed in real clothes (not pajamas!) at your usual time. This may sound insignificant but it helps you plan mentally for the day ahead and get into the mindset of &ldquo;I&rsquo;m going to work.&rdquo; Make A Work Space At Your Home: Though staying in bed or sitting on your sofa is relaxing, those who work successfully from home agree you &lsquo;re best off setting up a station. Choose your dining-room table if you don&rsquo;t have a seat. It allows you to maintain a healthy attitude, avoid distractions, and leave your job behind at the end of the day. Take Short Breaks: Take advantage of working from home. Take short breaks during work hours. It may seem unnecessary to take breaks, research has shown that taking short breaks can actually improve productivity and innovation. Be In Touch With Your Colleagues: If you are working in a team, make sure that you check in frequently just as you would at the workplace. Create to-do lists to keep yourself organized and focused and share the status of your lists with your supervisor. Stay Positive: This time will pass soon. Stay positive while working from home. If you will keep your mind positive, you will eventually start putting more effort into your work. You will become more dedicated to your work no matter where you are working from.</p>', '5-tips-to-work-effectively-from-home', 15, 9, 'post_main57.jpg', 'post_thumb57.jpg', 'post_list57.jpg', 2, 1, 1, 0, '2020-07-11 06:02:08', '2020-08-05 02:22:42');

